snippet.textDisplay:
People don’t understand how monumental it is for 2 Latina/Hispanic women to perform in Spanish and English during the biggest masculine sporting events in the United States of America. This performance represented ethnic culture and traditional mestizo roots. Literally in tears. As a young Latina growing up listening to Shakira in Spanish, ONLY , and now seeing her perform in my native tongue; shows me that anything is possible. To have Jbalvin and Bad Bunny two of the biggest current reggeaton stars sing only in Spanish is amazing. This is what the United States of AMERICA is all about, multicultural exposure.
The day is coming when not only African/Caribbean or Latino cultures are highlighted but when various cultures and countries are voiced/represented in the media.
